Feline2::
She looked at FZ and Squizzy. "I died? And now I'm back?" She had no 
recollection of her death. "Where is HotRod?"

Squizzy::
"Yes, she is ready. But not all of her memory is intact. Some of her 
memory chips and motherboard was damaged. She'll be fine, but someone 
else will have to help her fill in the gaps. She's ready to be take 
out if you need her to go with you."
